{
 "name": "RPlog_Ecks_File_-_AR-01_-_Promise_of_Pleasure",
 "title": "Ecks File AR-01: Promise of Pleasure",
 "summary": "On the bustling Concourse of Nar Shaddaa's entertainment district, the agent Kracen Ecks waits impatiently for a contact who never shows, only to be struck dumb by the sight of Ka'una, a striking four-lekku twi'lek engineer drifting through the crowd. After Ka'una deftly deflects a drunken admirer with a salacious story that sends him chasing off to another club, she catches Ecks staring and, amused, joins him for a drink at a sidewalk cafe. The two flirt and spar verbally: Ecks plays the awestruck tourist whose business meeting fell through, while Ka'una teases out that he plainly doesn't belong, revealing she dances as a hobby and works as an engineer aboard the orbiting cruiseliner Angry Rancor. Just as Ecks warms to the idea of a proper vacation aboard her ship, his datapad buzzes with another appointment, and he reluctantly rises to leave, pleasure deferred for business. He departs charmed, pressing her in vain to confirm the truth of her earlier scandalous tale, while Ka'una only smirks and toasts him goodbye, both clearly hoping to meet again.",
